subproject.description: Support to the further upstream movement of UNDPs operations and delivery of policy related services at country level in the organisation’s identified focus areas (pro-poor policies, democratic governance, HIV/AIDS, sustainable energy and environment, crisis prevention and recovery and ICT for development). Provide strategic policy analysis support to the programme section, analysis of development opportunities in the focus areas of UNDP, develop, deliver and mainstream specific policy related instruments, services and advocacy tools into national development initiatives.
subproject.title: Strategic Support to Developme

subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
